# Supercronic crontab for WordPress cron events.
#
# WP-Cron is disabled at the application level (DISABLE_WP_CRON=true in .env /
# Doppler) so WordPress never self-triggers cron on page load.  This file drives
# it externally instead, which is the correct approach for containerised deploys.
#
# The WP_CRON_INTERVAL env var lets you override the schedule at runtime without
# rebuilding the image (supercronic re-reads the file on SIGHUP, but env-var
# substitution is handled at startup by the shell wrapper below if needed).
# Default: every 5 minutes.
#
# Format: standard 5-field cron  (min hour dom month dow)

*/5 * * * * /usr/local/bin/wp-cron-run
